casebody.data:
Fadi AL-MAQALEH, et al.
v.
Chuck HAGEL, Secretary of Defense, et al. No. 14-6575 R46-003. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 29, 2014.

Opinion

The petition for writ of certiorari only as to Fadi al-Maqaleh and Amin al-Bakri was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.
